dfischer.utils

Class AlertConfigNotificationPeriodicIntervalAvResponseTimePerPageExceeded

  • java.lang.Object
    • dfischer.utils.AlertConfigGenericNotification
      • dfischer.utils.AlertConfigGenericCancelableNotification
        • dfischer.utils.AlertConfigNotificationPeriodicIntervalAvResponseTimePerPageExceeded

  • public class AlertConfigNotificationPeriodicIntervalAvResponseTimePerPageExceeded
extends AlertConfigGenericCancelableNotification
    Configuration data for alert notification: limit of average response time per page exceeded during test execution.
     
    Specific placeholders:
    • {$avResponseTimePerPageLimit}: the configured average response time limit per page in seconds
    • {$avResponseTimePerPage}: the actual average response time per page in seconds
